DNS in Nodejs

How install

	$ mkdir /opt/fun_dns
	$ cd /opt/fun_dns
	$ tar xvf /path/to/fun_dns.tar.gz
	$ ln -s /opt/fun_dns/fun_dns /etc/init.d
	$ update-rc.d fun_dns defaults
	$ #Start service
	$ service fun_dns start	

How define hostname
edit 'conf.ini', put
[hostname]
ip= your ip4 addresse

Server confiurations(serv.ini)
host = your ip4 addresse to listen(if not defined listen all)
port = port to listen(if not defined listen 53)

